{"tid":1591934,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"航機手提氧氣樽壓力偏低　國泰港龍調查後解僱兩員工","createTime":"2019-09-24T11:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T16:01:50.000Z","uid":726,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"99b0edbeefaa950996c420b8e98c445d1be98e8d","tid":1591934,"uid":726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:17:39.000Z","msg":"航機手提氧氣樽壓力偏低　國泰港龍調查後解僱兩員工　<br />\n2019-09-24 HKT 18:08<br />\n<br />\n國泰港龍航空證實，星期六為吉隆坡前往香港的KA730航班例行檢查，發現一個手提氧氣樽壓力偏低，國泰港龍表示，嚴正處理事件，所有執勤航班的機艙服務員，均被暫停飛行職務，協助調查，並按調查結果解僱兩名機艙服務員。<br />\n<br />\n國泰港龍航空表示，涉事航班是空中巴士A330客機，機艙内總共有16個手提氧氣樽，手提氧氣樽專供執勤的機組人員使用，讓他們在飛機氣壓急降的情況下，依然能在機艙內行動，機組人員及乘客的座位上均裝有應急時使用的個人氧氣面罩。<br />\n<br />\n國泰港龍航空表示，事後已立即為氧氣樽重新充氣，事件中沒有任何機組人員及乘客安全受到任何影響，亦已向香港警方報案，警方就事件同步調查，並已知會民航處。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482337-20190924.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482337-20190924.htm&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=a5e52886\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482337-20190924.htm&h=fb51c1e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482337-20190924.htm</a>"},{"pid":"31c0e5c9c5a44a358818219547067f2a2b4d5e15","tid":1591934,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"3830b917e692ecf3c384a0adbcafefa4bbbdc7b6","tid":1591934,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"大陸人？"},{"pid":"37b5b4a5785146b734f0d4e3f3049769075f5f61","tid":1591934,"uid":189652,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy